<HEADLINE> Mbeki, Winnie Mandela Nominated as ANC Leaders </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, September 14 (Xinhua) -- South African deputy
president Thabo Mbeki and parliament member Winnie
Madikizela-Mandela have been nominated as the president and
deputy president of the ruling African National Congress (ANC).
</P>
