has announced that he will retire from the party's presidency at
the ANC's national congress to be held in December.
</P>
<P>
Winnie Mandela, ex-wife of President Mandela, is currently
president of ANC woman's league.
</P>
<P>
The league will forward its nominations to the ANC's national
executive committee, the party's top policy-making body. 
