former president Heshemi Rafsanjani, new President Mohammad
Khatami and Foreign Minister Kamal Kharrazi have sent messages of
condolence to Sheikh Hassan Nasrallah, Lebanese Iran-backed
Hezbollah's Secretary-General, for the killing of his son by
Israeli troops in south Lebanon last Friday night.
</P>
