has an area of about 1,570 square meters. It was bought by Rillex
Investment Limited for 51 million HK dollars (6.54 million U.S.
dollars).
</P>
<P>
On the site, which is intended for private residential use,
excluding service apartment, the developer has to complete a gross
floor area of no less than 377 square meters on or before
September 30, 2000. 
