<HEADLINE> German Communist Party Congratulates CPC on Congress </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 15 (Xinhua) -- The German Communist Party
has sent a congratulatory message to the Communist Party of China
(CPC) on its 15th National Congress.
</P>
<P>
In the telegram to CPC Central Committee General Secretary
Jiang Zemin, Chairman of the German Communist Party Heinz Stehr
said, "We pay close attention to your creativeness and efforts
during the course of building Socialism with Chinese
characteristics."
</P>
<P>
"Your party has enriched the theory and practice of Marxism,"
said he. 
