<HEADLINE> Moroccan Party Congratulates CPC on Congress </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 15 (Xinhua) -- The Socialist Union of
Popular Forces (SUPF) of Morocco has sent a congratulatory message
to the Communist Party of China (CPC) on its 15th National
Congress.
</P>
