<DOCNO> XIE19970915.0154 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-15 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Diary of Party Congress Delegates (Sept. 15) - 2 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The culture with Chinese characteristics is not rooted in
desert or sterile land, but has developed through inheritance,
reforms and development of Chinese traditional culture.
</P>
<P>
Yet our national culture comprises both the cream and dross.
Aimed at building socialist culture, we should discard the dross
and select the essential through careful analysis and study.
</P>
<P>
Socialist culture with Chinese characteristics not only
reflects the basic features of socialist economy and politics, but
lends a great impetus to their advance as well.
</P>
<P>
Dialectical understanding of the inter-relationship among
economics, politics and culture is one of the viewpoints of the
historical materialism.
</P>
<P>
It is based on this very understanding that we believe that the
building of socialist culture with Chinese characteristics cannot
be separated from the overall cause of building socialism with
Chinese characteristics.
</P>
<P>
At present, China is at an important historical period of
inheriting the past and ushering the future, and all fields,
including economic, political and social life, are undergoing fast
and profound reforms and development, thus putting forward
extremely urgent tasks and providing extremely rich materials for
the building of socialist culture.
</P>
<P>
Once the above mentioned two aspects are combined, I believe
that a socialist culture featuring characteristics of both the
nation and the time will be guaranteed, enabling it to become a
kind of scientific, popular and national socialist culture serving
the modernization drive and the needs of the world and the future.
</P>
<P>
With a new century right on the corner, we are fully confident
of the future of China.
</P>
<P>
We should set our sights high not only over the economic
construction, but also over the cultural progress as well just as
what Jiang said in his report: "In the great practice of the
socialist modernization drive, we are sure to create a more
magnificent socialist culture with Chinese characteristics and
make due contribution to human civilization."  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970915.0155 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-09-15 </DATE_TIME>
