<HEADLINE> India's Inflation Declines Marginally </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, September 15 (Xinhua) -- India's annual inflation
dropped marginally by 0.1 percentage points to 3.81 percent for
the week that ended on August 30 from 3.91 percent the previous
week, the Times of India said today.
</P>
