the impact of the September 1 increase in prices of petroleum
products feeds in.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the wholesale price index (WPI) for "all
commodities" recorded a rise of 0.1 percent to 327.1 during the
week under review against 326.9 the week before.  
