<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, September 15 (Xinhua) -- At least 32 people were
killed and 29 others injured when an intercity bus collided
head-on Sunday with a dump truck on the Cakung-Cijunir toll road,
East Jakarta, police sources here said today.
</P>
<P>
Most of the dead were believed to be passengers on the bus
which was traveling from Jakarta to Purwodadi in Central Java,
when it collided with the truck from the opposite direction,
police said.
