<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, September 14 (Xinhua) -- Tim Henman of Britain
dismissed Marc Rosset of Switzerland in straight sets to win the
President's Cup tennis tournament in Tashkent, Uzbekistan on
Sunday.
</P>
<P>
